profile.bio: Is your mouth tiny and small? Then why dont you come down to our lil' bits. Where the food is tiny, it looks like regular food but really tiny, you can put it in your mouth and eat it. Nothing gets stuck in your lips. Its just tiny and tiny and fits right in. We got tiny little lasagna, tiny pizza, tiny pie, & little tiny fryed eggs. Oh shit, we got tiny people. You hungry? come on down. Eat some f*ing shit you f*ing stupid bitch...just kiding.
